headline: Federal Realty Investment Trust to Present at Citi's 2025 30th Annual Global Property CEO Conference
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE: FRT) announced today that the Company will present at the Citi's 2025 Global Property CEO Conference on Monday, March 3, 2025 from 8:10 AM ET to 8:45 AM ET.
